{
  "stem": "12666.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tried to show films too so that they would-- they would see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because many people did not believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't believe that such a Western nation, Western civilization, would do things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many people were very skeptical about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, I know we, we were helping the German population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So food was brought in, because there were shortages of food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we always liked to dress in civilian, take off our uniform and in civilian to go to a German pub and have some beer, and sometimes listen to the conversation of those Bavarians, you know?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we marched into a pub, we got a table, we got our beer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right next to us, there was a group of Bavarian sitting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one in a loud voice would say, hey, did you see that American propaganda?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They says, what? what? what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They says, did you-- did you know that that butter that they brought here to bring it to us had American wrapping, but it was really the German butter?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They were skeptical of our foreign aid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they looked upon us and they suddenly switched the conversation, and we didn't know why.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the American clothing cut is different than the German cut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even the shoes are different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they looked at us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even if we did speak German, you know, they knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And so they switched the conversation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was very interesting, you know, to listen to some of the comments.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They didn't even believe in the foreign aid that was coming in to feed them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's really amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, some of the trials were over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they needed reviewers to review the, the material that was printed in many, many volumes.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
